      "description": "FEA ensemble predictions compared against N=11 experimental constructs. All QoI differences within 10% acceptance bound; E/uval < 1.96 for all three quantities of interest.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/cb-validation-analysis",
