    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against a required level of 3 due to evaluation under a single static load condition; this gap is accepted given the scope of the regulatory submission and the strength of evidence across all other factors. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the intended regulatory decision for the non-cannulated pedicle screw design.",
